  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >'B.o.W II VR' is a VR only, sports-based action arcade game. In this story driven adventure you, the player, will expand on the diving skills already taught during its prequel, by culling Invasive species, exploring underwater cave systems, deep dive using trimix, as well as visit the artic circle, and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This exciting sequel now includes an updated and enhanced deluxe version of the original game 'Bodies of Water' also!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Suitable for players aged 13 years or over.</p>",
